========
gg_roman_ggn
The aim of this map was to create a very lifelike map, while retaining the fun of a gungame.
Features a large parthenon like building with intricate architecture. There are several ramps on each corner of the building that allows access to the top of the building. There is no current 3D skybox, in a future version i may include one.
========
